Lottobits

This is a lottery and gambling system that anonymously utilizes ticket purchases through the transaction hash on the cryptocurrency blockchain, we are starting with lottery and critter game.

How it works

The player deposits the ticket amount into the altcoin address of the day's game, and enters the transaction hash in the database along with the altcoin address information to receive the prize if he wins the draw.
This is generated through the transaction hash, a single thousand ticket number, and thus the game becomes irreversible, all done directly with altcoins anonymously.
Our draw takes place every day, and each draw of the day is assigned a different bitcoin address. The prize winner will receive it directly at the bitcoin address entered on their profile.

Only bitcoin transactions sent to the address presented in the game will be awarded, so the player must enter the hash tx of the transaction he has made, otherwise the system will not reward.

Lottery Rules

Who wins:
    - One of the 5 numbers drawn for the main prizes
    - Thousands, hundreds and tens of any of the numbers drawn in the top 5 prizes
    - Tickets whose numbers contain the final dozen identical to one of the previous 3 dozen or the last dozen to the tenth dozen of the number drawn for prize 1, except for the winners for the previous and subsequent 
    approximation.
    - The first prize unit.

We run our code on the deep web, and open it to the community to help and play

